debutant — licence placeholder
==============================

A formal licence has not yet been chosen for debutant. Until one
is selected and committed in this file, the contents of this
repository are made available for review, discussion, and
collaboration with the contributors named in git history only.

Contributors and reviewers: please treat this directory as if it
were under no explicit licence. Do not redistribute, fork for
public republication, or build derivative works until a licence
is committed here. Contributions submitted while this placeholder
is in place are understood to be relicensable under whichever
licence is ultimately chosen.

This file will be replaced with the chosen licence text once the
decision is made.
